{{Quote|I won't pretend to know the deep-rooted sociological or psychological underpinnings of our success. Let's face it. People in our sector just feel lucky.|Kalasaad Woztu, on the successes of the casinos|<ref name="HNN">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|52|business/13418_1.html|Leisure Industry Suffers Record Losses}}</ref>}}
'''Kalasaad Woztu''' was the [[Prime Minister/Legends|Prime Minister]] of<ref name="HNN" /> the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]]<ref name="Planet">''[[Geonosis and the Outer Rim Worlds]]''</ref> [[Vorzyd V/Legends|Vorzyd V]], which was famous for its [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]],<ref name="HNN" /> by [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. In the same [[Standard year/Legends|year]],<ref name="Date">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|52|business/13418_1.html|Leisure Industry Suffers Record Losses}} is set on the date 13:4:18, which corresponds to [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] according to the reasoning [[Template:YearMathGRS|here]].</ref> the [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] tourism industry declined, decreasing the number of tourists visiting usually crowded vacation spots. [[Casino/Legends|Casinos]], including the ones managed by Woztu, were not affected by the drop in business. In an interview published in the [[HoloNet News CoCo District Edition|CoCo District Edition]] of the [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]], Woztu reflected that the beings in the [[Vorzyd sector/Legends|Vorzyd sector]] felt [[luck]]y amidst the downturn.<ref name="HNN" />

==Behind the scenes==
Kalasaad Woztu appeared in "Leisure Industry Suffers Record Losses," an article<ref name="HNN" /> written by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[Paul Ens]]<ref name="credits">{{HoloNetNewsWeb||credits.html|Credits}}</ref> and published in [[HoloNet News Vol. 531 52|''HoloNet News Vol. 531'' #52]] on the [[HoloNet News (original website)|HoloNet News website]]<ref name="HNN" /> on [[April 18]], [[2002]].<ref name="HNN52 date">{{JCFCite|url=posts/6493893|board=Literature|thread=The Official HoloNetNews Discussion Thread|user=IAmTheDarkSide|date=2002-04-18|time=6:27 PM|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220914072939/https://boards.theforce.net/threads/the-official-holonetnews-discussion-thread.5990764/page-11#post-6493893}}</ref>

